<div id="review_259751891" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/259751891" />
    <a title="Dede" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3777047-dede"><img alt="Dede" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1274754127p2/3777047.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/259751891?book_show_action=true">Jan 10, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Dede" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Dede" href="/user/show/3777047-dede">Dede</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition 9781941212066" href="/book/show/13229281-widow-virgin-whore">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer259751891" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3915879671902601610">Widow, Virgin, Whore is a novel of three women, each at a different stage in their life. They move in together and as time progresses, their differences become their strengths as each member faces the challenges caused when Darla is diagnosed with AIDS. Having lost several friends to the AIDS virus, I found the description of the virus and treatment to be very accurate. This is a moving story of friendship, family, growth and loss. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

