        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1431812837" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3914498606134273395">I picked this book by its title-what a cool title for chic lit heartwarming drama! But Blah!<br/>I was disappointed that this book writes like AIDS is a new disease, not been around 30 years! <br/>As for the story, predictable simple writing and wished it focused less on the disease and more on the people.<br/><br/> </span>

          </span>
        </div>


