<div id="review_359730256" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/359730256" />
    <a title="Lillian Jade" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7399236-lillian-jade"><img alt="Lillian Jade" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1337819131p2/7399236.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/359730256?book_show_action=true">Jul 02, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lillian Jade" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lillian Jade" href="/user/show/7399236-lillian-jade">Lillian Jade</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition 9781941212066" href="/book/show/13229281-widow-virgin-whore">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer359730256" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9370389712176262862">This book comes with all the baggage one might expect from the perspective of three woman characters. I was expecting more smut from the title, rather than the emotion the story pulled from me. I became attached to Katherine, and when Darla was diagnosed with aids, it broadened my knowledge to a depth that I was unprepared for. Tragedy strikes as the woman form a very real binding friendship with one another. A story of the suffering Aids brings which was beautifully written.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


